value.diagram:
flowchart TD
A[What are you trying to do?] --> B{Need ordering only?}
B -->|Yes| C[Use references or depends_on]
B -->|No| D{Need to alter replacement behavior?}
D -->|Yes| E[Use lifecycle block]
E --> E1[create_before_destroy]
E --> E2[prevent_destroy]
E --> E3[ignore_changes]
E --> E4[replace_triggered_by]
D -->|No| F{Existing unmanaged resource?}
F -->|Yes| G[Use import block and possibly terraform query]
F -->|No| H{Address changed?}
H -->|Yes| I[Use moved block]
H -->|No| J{Stop managing without deleting?}
J -->|Yes| K[Use removed block]

